name: MSRI-ONE-PRSP-GIFRYBV-OB-01
description: v4w.enko - "MSRI-ONE-PRSP-GIFRYBV-OV-01" is a perspectice projection gif animation of  3d Object, generated with custom definition. 4 lofts are animated in 4 layers for each color: Red, Yellow, Blue, Violet. The cells of the Violet "3d voronoi" cube are linked to the attractor`s points of the lofts. Another one group of cells linked to the same attractor points  are rotating as the Orange  cube .  The Perspective projection. Total 128frames, 1024*1024px canvas.
